- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper involves analyzing a large dataset of user-contributed guitar tablatures. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possibility as the paper examines usage patterns of chords and lyrics across different regions, genres, and eras. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a potential category as the paper involves analyzing associations between lyrics and chord categories. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possibility as the paper deals with analyzing music and lyrics.
